      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Christine Tacon marks final week in role as GCA
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Christine Tacon will step down as Groceries Code Adjudicator (GCA) at the end of this week. </p>

  </div>
</div>

